mathematica: nmax = 53; CoefficientList[Series[Product[(1 - x^k)^PartitionsQ[k], {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]
a[n_] := a[n] = If[n == 0, 1, Sum[-Sum[d PartitionsQ[d], {d, Divisors[k]}] a[n - k], {k, 1, n}]/n]; Table[a[n], {n, 0, 53}]
